title: Culture - Chanting On (Compilation) 2007 TQMP [FLAC]
description:
Info from Distributors' Website:

"Originally appearing in 2004, the compilation album CHANTING ON is back in this Sanctuary re-release. CHANTING ON celebrates the best of roots reggae legends, Culture, bringing together 18 of the group's most powerful songs recorded during Culture's ...    Full Descriptiontenure with Ras Records in the 1990s. CHANTING ON provides a portrait of one of reggae's most vital protest acts during an important and somewhat overlooked phase in its career"
